---
---

<section class="section" id="contact">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">聯絡我哋</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">歡迎透過 WhatsApp 或致電查詢</p>
    <div class="contact-grid">
      <div class="contact-info">
        <div class="contact-item">
          <span class="contact-icon">📍</span>
          <div>
            <h3>地址</h3>
            <p>香港深水埗長沙灣道226號<br />深之都1樓230號鋪</p>
            <p class="contact-note">深水埗站 D2 出口，賽馬會側</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-item">
          <span class="contact-icon">📞</span>
          <div>
            <h3>電話 / WhatsApp</h3>
            <p><a href="tel:+85269960711" onclick="gtag('event','phone_click',{event_category:'contact',event_label:'contact_section'})">6996 0711</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-item">
          <span class="contact-icon">🕐</span>
          <div>
            <h3>營業時間</h3>
            <p>每日 12:00 - 21:00</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="https://wa.me/85269960711?text=%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E6%83%B3%E8%A9%A2%E5%95%8F%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E7%B6%AD%E4%BF%AE%E5%A0%B1%E5%83%B9%E3%80%82%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%9E%8B%E8%99%9F%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%9A" class="btn btn-whatsapp contact-cta" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
          onclick="gtag('event','whatsapp_click',{event_category:'contact',event_label:'contact_section'})">
          💬 WhatsApp 即時查詢
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-map">
        <iframe
          src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d1844.2!2d114.1618173!3d22.3314439!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x340401b0db7b8a9f%3A0x3af9fc78da4b5316!2sMONCITY!5e0!3m2!1szh-HK!2shk!4v1"
          width="100%"
          height="100%"
          style="border:0; border-radius: var(--radius-lg); min-height: 300px;"
          allowfullscreen=""
          loading="lazy"
          referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
          title="MonCity 手機維修地圖位置"
        ></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .contact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .contact-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .contact-icon { font-size: 1.6rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .contact-item h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .contact-item p { color: var(--ink-muted); line-height: 1.6; }
  .contact-note { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--ink-soft); margin-top: 4px; }
  .contact-cta { margin-top: 8px; text-align: center; justify-content: center; width: 100%; }
  .contact-map { min-height: 350px; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 32px; }
  }
</style>
